{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01WJVfCJ2Pjiaz1LGuzYWqXA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The pod is running but the readiness probe is failing with HTTP 503. This is because CockroachDB pods need to be initialized via `cockroach init` before the cluster becomes ready. The `/health?ready=1` probe returns 503 until the cluster is initialized.\n\nAlso I notice only one pod is running - crdb-cluster-0. The other pods (crdb-cluster-1, crdb-cluster-2) haven't even started. This might be because:\n1. The StatefulSet creates pods one at a time, and waits for the previous one to be Ready before creating the next. Since the readiness probe is failing, pod-0 is never Ready, so pod-1 never gets created.\n2. There's a chicken-and-egg problem here: the pods can't become Ready until the cluster is initialized, but the cluster can't be initialized until enough pods are running.\n\nThe fix is to change the StatefulSet to use `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` so all three pods start simultaneously, then run `cockroach init` on one of them to initialize the cluster. So the solution is to switch the StatefulSet to parallel pod management so all three pods start simultaneously, then once they're all running, I'll initialize the cluster on one of them and they should all become ready.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":558,"cache_read_input_tokens":31947,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":558},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"72bce601-3a3f-4730-b16b-22d47db88613","uuid":"0446563c-ad1c-4f7d-bd7c-57929584af77","request_id":"req_011CccAbceTBB8Jf5v2ZDNgJ"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01WJVfCJ2Pjiaz1LGuzYWqXA","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The readiness probe returns 503 because `cockroach init` hasn't been run. The default `OrderedReady` policy means pod-1 and pod-2 never start since pod-0 can't become Ready pre-init. I need to switch to `Parallel` pod management, then run `cockroach init`."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":558,"cache_read_input_tokens":31947,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":558},"output_tokens":32,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"72bce601-3a3f-4730-b16b-22d47db88613","uuid":"c5858dcc-28e3-4aea-80c4-913d83dfa8a3","request_id":"req_011CccAbceTBB8Jf5v2ZDNgJ"}
